# {{.Name}} ({{.Type}})

{{ .Description | trimspace }}

~> **Singleton Resource — Known Terraform Best-Practice Violation**
This resource is a singleton. There should only ever be **one** `{{.Name}}` block
in your entire Terraform configuration. It manages the global Unbound DNS resolver
settings on your OPNsense appliance rather than creating discrete objects.
This design is a known violation of Terraform's resource model and best practices.
It is provided intentionally because the ability to manage these settings via
Terraform has value despite the trade-off.

