## Import

This resource **cannot be created** via `terraform apply`. You must import it
before it can be managed. The import ID is always the fixed string `unbound_settings`.

In Terraform v1.5.0 and later, use an [`import` block](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/language/import):

```terraform
import {
  to = {{.Name}}.settings
  id = "unbound_settings"
}
```

Using `terraform import`:

```console
% terraform import {{.Name}}.settings unbound_settings
```

~> **Note on destroy**
Running `terraform destroy` (or removing this resource from your configuration)
will only remove it from Terraform state. The upstream Unbound configuration on
your OPNsense appliance will **not** be deleted or reset.
